# Flutter output

## Must

- `dart analyze` clean
- `lib/features/<slug>/`, shared `lib/widgets/`
- Null-safe, modular, `const` where sensible
- Theme and spacing tokens ‚Äî no random inline colors, padding, or radii
- Use `AppColors`, `AppTextStyles`, `AppSpacing`, `AppRadius`, `AppElevation` from `lib/theme/`

## Avoid

- Giant nested Column/Row without extraction
- Duplicated subtrees ‚Äî extract a widget file
- Fixed-width-only where flex should adapt

## After build / fix

```bash
cd <project_dir> && dart analyze && dart format .
```

App logic may live in dedicated handlers or stubs ‚Äî layout still follows plan and theme.
